author: stsp
msg: the new type from the conflict callback for now.
Note that there is a behaviour change here:
generate_propconflict() didn't use the description2 type in the same
way read_prop_conflict_descs() did because it puts the incoming property
value into 'their_abspath' and the .prej file contents into 'merged_file',
rather than the other way around as read_prop_conflict_descs() did.
As of this commit, all inconsistencies should be consistent again :)
I will just call this a "bug fix".
